headline: U.S. ByteDance investors looking into TikTok U.S. deal, FT reports

headline: A Trump plan for TikTok is coming together — and Oracle may play a starring role
summary: Chinese tech giant ByteDance has roughly two weeks to save its video app TikTok from a renewed US ban — and there are signs cloud computing giant Oracle may play a prominent role.

headline: Better Artificial Intelligence (AI) Stock: Oracle vs. Dell
summary: This huge spending is going to be a tailwind for Oracle (NYSE: ORCL) and Dell Technologies (NYSE: DELL), two tech giants that are already benefiting from the huge outlay on AI infrastructure.  While Oracle is down 10% so far in 2025, Dell is down by 16%.  Oracle has traditionally been known for providing database management software, but AI has opened a whole new growth opportunity for the company.
